 # Kubernetes RBAC Documentation (Group-Based Access)

## Objective
Implement group-based access control in Kubernetes using RBAC:
- development group → pods & deployments access
- testing group → services access
- Namespace: team3-ns

---

## Concept
- Kubernetes does NOT manage users internally
- Authentication is done using certificates
- Groups are assigned using:
  O = group-name
- RBAC maps groups to permissions

---

